snippet.title: I made a horror game in one month ( Part 1)
snippet.description:
Wishlist Evil Corporation: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2672260/Evil_Corporation/

Join Discord:Soon :D

Follow on X:
Also Soon :)

Follow on TikTok:Very Soon ;)

Unreal Engine 5 is a state-of-the-art real-time 3D creation platform with really awesome features like Nanite, which enables high-fidelity models, and Lumen, facilitating dynamic lighting simulations. And that’s really cool.

Evil Corporation is combination of my two lovely games and I hope you will also play my game on Steam :)
